      "name": "store_memory",
      "description": "Store a fact in memory, so that it can be used in future code generation or review tasks. The fact should be a clear and concise statement about conventions, structure, logic, usage, or preferences. It may be based on the code itself or on information provided by the user.",
      "parameters": {
